The announcement of the New Green Savings programme was a positive signal for our construction industry, especially for small and medium-sized companies in individual regions.
It is a great opportunity not only for citizens, who save considerable amounts on heating after the implementation of the measures, but also an opportunity for construction companies and manufacturers of building materials.
